This team can be almost every legitimate scenario (there's only 1 scenario that the team has trouble winning).

Also, be warned: it took me a long time to put together this team and pretty much contains stat values that should not be changed.  
(You don't want to bring up the strength, constitution, or armor up too much or you'll get a team with negative health values.  Also, 
bringing the dexteriority up is probably a very bad idea.)  Please also note:  for the most part, you'll have trouble using up all that mana 
for any character on this team unless time is frozen.
